Bog-Pods proprietary Switcheroo Shooting System enables replacement of either shooting rest with other interchangeable accessories in the Switcheroo system. The Q-Stik monopod features a three-section adjustable aluminum leg and an all-terrain rubber foot that unscrews to reveal a carbide tip for enhanced traction on ice.
